quote.summary: Shanghai Iluvatar CoreX Semiconductor Co Ltd is a China-based company principally engaged in the sale and development of general-purpose computing on graphics processing units (GPGPU) products and artificial intelligence (AI) computing solutions. The Company’s portfolio of GPGPU products include chips and accelerators for both training and inference scenarios. The Company’s AI computing solutions include purpose-built GPGPU servers and scalable GPGPU clusters. The Company’s products and solutions are mainly used in financial services, healthcare, retail, education and other fields. The Company is also engaged in providing technology services. The Company mainly conducts its business in the domestic market.
